{"tid":404401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一個傷害中華民族感情既例子","createTime":"2017-09-18T05:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T05:59:21.000Z","uid":18679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81b04fa158d57e133b12c38f59b3b9804a89bdaa","tid":404401,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"2015年王愈超（John Wang）等人在《Zoological Studies》發表研究，認為中華白海豚可以分為「中華白海豚」（Sousa chinensis chinensis）與「臺灣白海豚」（Sousa chinensis taiwanensis）兩個亞種，兩者的斑點圖樣幾乎完全不同，兩者在地理區隔與動物行為上也不同。[8][9]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22d933882e6d319d1d5f431fdde64d0f8257d4f","tid":404401,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"大家都係起到游，唔洗分咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6228ac3db2ee4302e39541ec18f72cd3686578c7","tid":404401,"uid":18679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T05:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}